[5 months later]

6
00:00:50,160 --> 00:00:54,450
You haven't memorized the 100 important words I marked out for you, have you?

7
00:00:54,450 --> 00:00:58,660
Yes... I'm sorry.

8
00:00:58,660 --> 00:01:00,160
This won't work.

9
00:01:00,160 --> 00:01:04,040
I can only call your mom.

10
00:01:04,040 --> 00:01:07,170
No, you can't do that. You know my mom.

11
00:01:07,170 --> 00:01:09,420
She won't forgive me.

12
00:01:11,570 --> 00:01:14,630
So I told you to study hard.

13
00:01:14,630 --> 00:01:17,560
You're already a high school student.

14
00:01:19,430 --> 00:01:21,580
I don't want to study.

15
00:01:25,160 --> 00:01:26,530
Sit properly.

16
00:01:26,530 --> 00:01:29,390
I'll start from the third reading question.

17
00:01:36,810 --> 00:01:38,289
Goodness.

18
00:01:38,289 --> 00:01:40,880
Didn't I tell you to turn it off during class?

19
00:01:40,880 --> 00:01:43,979
Sir, he's my only friend.

20
00:01:43,979 --> 00:01:45,340
He's my only friend.

21
00:01:45,340 --> 00:01:47,600
Please forgive me this time.

22
00:01:49,520 --> 00:01:52,090
Okay, let's take a ten minute break.

23
00:01:52,090 --> 00:01:54,920
Great. Thank you.

24
00:02:06,720 --> 00:02:10,280
I know it's ridiculous. I know.

25
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:11,740
You know?

26
00:02:12,870 --> 00:02:16,300
But we are graduating soon.

27
00:02:16,300 --> 00:02:19,040
I don't want to deny my feelings.

28
00:02:19,820 --> 00:02:21,829
If you want,

29
00:02:21,829 --> 00:02:24,340
I will never see you again.

30
00:02:29,210 --> 00:02:31,560
How could you do this to me...

31
00:02:54,460 --> 00:02:55,750
Wait.

32
00:02:57,350 --> 00:02:59,579
Are you saying if we don't date...

33
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:03,770
I'll never see you again?

34
00:03:04,710 --> 00:03:08,270
How could you say that to me?

35
00:03:08,270 --> 00:03:10,330
What else can I say in this situation?

36
00:03:10,330 --> 00:03:11,660
What is this situation then?

37
00:03:11,660 --> 00:03:13,850
It's all over.

38
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:17,640
It's all over?

39
00:03:20,190 --> 00:03:23,460
So you'll never see me again?

40
00:03:25,220 --> 00:03:28,360
You're giving up on me for that stupid reason?

41
00:03:38,579 --> 00:03:39,300
[Delivery order received]

42
00:03:43,030 --> 00:03:44,310
Let's go.

43
00:03:45,720 --> 00:03:49,520
"Economics in Society" elective class,

44
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:53,579
due to a welcoming party for freshmen,

45
00:03:53,579 --> 00:03:56,220
will be moved to 6 p.m. on Friday instead.

46
00:03:57,180 --> 00:04:00,820
[Notice
The class for the first semester of 2023 will be moved to 6 p.m. next Friday instead.
