47
00:04:17,149 --> 00:04:19,839
Call me when you have collected your thoughts.

48
00:04:38,220 --> 00:04:40,340
[Pass the Entrance Test with Flying Colors]

49
00:05:11,410 --> 00:05:12,880
Are you okay?

50
00:05:14,670 --> 00:05:15,900
Yes.

51
00:05:18,090 --> 00:05:19,530
Senior.

52
00:05:20,840 --> 00:05:22,040
What?

53
00:05:23,380 --> 00:05:25,690
I major in business too.

54
00:05:25,690 --> 00:05:28,490
I haven't seen you before.

55
00:05:28,490 --> 00:05:32,550
I didn't attend the entrance ceremony and welcome party.

56
00:05:32,550 --> 00:05:34,630
I'm entering class of 2022, Seo Hanjoon.

57
00:05:35,890 --> 00:05:38,760
Really? Nice to meet you.

58
00:05:38,760 --> 00:05:43,420
But senior, your eyes are...

59
00:05:43,420 --> 00:05:45,620
You mean this?

60
00:05:45,620 --> 00:05:48,220
I'm in the boxing club.

61
00:05:48,220 --> 00:05:50,480
I like boxing too.

62
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,770
- Really? - Yes.

63
00:05:51,770 --> 00:05:53,700
- You like boxing too? - Yes.

64
00:05:53,700 --> 00:05:56,300
I can drop the honorifics right?

65
00:05:56,300 --> 00:05:58,290
Of course, senior.

66
00:05:58,290 --> 00:06:02,640
What senior? Just call me bro.

67
00:06:02,640 --> 00:06:05,760
In college life, social life is very important.

68
00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:08,000
There are many good freshmen this year too.

69
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:10,690
You must attend today's welcoming party.

70
00:06:10,690 --> 00:06:11,990
Okay?

71
00:06:11,990 --> 00:06:13,840
Okay, bro.

72
00:06:13,840 --> 00:06:14,770
See you.

73
00:06:14,770 --> 00:06:16,070
Okay.

74
00:06:16,070 --> 00:06:17,650
Take care.

75
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:23,830
Let's drink.

76
00:06:25,830 --> 00:06:26,970
Let's drink.

77
00:06:26,970 --> 00:06:29,210
It's your turn.

78
00:06:29,210 --> 00:06:30,620
No.

79
00:06:30,620 --> 00:06:32,560
Aren't we drinking together?

80
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:35,020
Drink.

81
00:06:35,020 --> 00:06:36,300
Give it to Jo Yoojae.

82
00:06:36,300 --> 00:06:38,080
Yes!

83
00:06:38,080 --> 00:06:46,580
Jo Yoojae. Jo Yoojae. Jo Yoojae.

84
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:53,510
Jo Yoojae. Jo Yoojae. Jo Yoojae.

85
00:06:54,930 --> 00:06:58,130
Seo Hanjoon isn't here today either.

86
00:06:58,130 --> 00:07:01,970
He's not hiding. He's basically missing, no?

87
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:04,600
I don't know what happened to him,

88
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:07,260
but he should at least come to get his graduation certificate.

89
00:07:07,260 --> 00:07:13,630
He's not a kid. He knows what he's doing.

90
00:07:13,630 --> 00:07:15,850
Did he fill in his college application?

91
00:07:15,850 --> 00:07:17,550
With his grades,

92
00:07:17,550 --> 00:07:19,280
he should be able to apply for Hanyong University or Munhwa University.

93
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:20,600
If not, Hanguk University?

94
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:22,180
I don't know either.

95
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:29,160
The atmosphere is weird.

96
00:07:57,220 --> 00:08:01,760
Oh...

97
00:08:04,290 --> 00:08:06,220
Let's see.

98
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:15,470
Are you Seo Hanjoon?

99
00:08:15,470 --> 00:08:18,090
I'm Jo Yoojae.

100
00:08:21,140 --> 00:08:22,650
Ah, right.

101
00:08:24,270 --> 00:08:25,540
Okay.

102
00:08:27,080 --> 00:08:28,560
What is it?

103
00:08:30,220 --> 00:08:36,320
Well... Can I take Seo Hanjoon's graduation certificate in his place?

104
00:08:37,400 --> 00:08:42,320
Oh... Graduation certificate.

105
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:45,710
Where is it?

106
00:08:45,710 --> 00:08:48,010
Graduation certificate.

107
00:08:54,560 --> 00:08:56,290
Here.

108
00:09:04,790 --> 00:09:10,190
Go see him

109
00:09:10,190 --> 00:09:12,690
and pass it to him.

110
00:09:12,690 --> 00:09:14,520
You're friends, right?

111
00:09:16,570 --> 00:09:18,940
- Okay. - Okay.

112
