♫ When I'm immersed in silence, when I close my eyes ♫

114
00:09:28,540 --> 00:09:32,040
♫ Huru came to my embrace and kissed me ♫

115
00:09:32,040 --> 00:09:35,590
♫ Pff, I feel its wet lips, ay ♫

116
00:09:35,590 --> 00:09:37,750
♫ This is my service area, after the event, ay ♫

117
00:09:37,750 --> 00:09:39,880
♫ When I leave the audience behind ♫

118
00:09:39,880 --> 00:09:42,120
♫ When I'm alone the sense of loneliness strikes, ay ♫

119
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:44,200
♫ Huru, when I'm playing the keyboard ♫

120
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:46,400
♫ Can you sit on the chair properly? ♫

121
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:48,600
♫ Thanks to Huru playing keyboard ♫

122
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:50,180
♫ Ballads became jazz ♫

123
00:09:50,180 --> 00:09:52,220
♫ After my first work, "photograph" ♫

124
00:09:52,220 --> 00:09:56,590
♫ And "My life is So Beautiful" after ♫

125
00:09:59,670 --> 00:10:02,760
What's wrong? Are you feeling uncomfortable anywhere?

126
00:10:03,830 --> 00:10:05,610
I miss my mom.

127
00:10:12,680 --> 00:10:14,910
Do you want to go home now?

128
00:10:17,410 --> 00:10:19,790
I live in Chuncheon.

129
00:10:24,370 --> 00:10:26,290
So you're living by yourself?

130
00:10:26,290 --> 00:10:27,650
Yes.

131
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:31,910
My mom is far away too.

132
00:10:32,890 --> 00:10:35,450
I miss my mom too.

133
00:10:44,040 --> 00:10:47,800
I heard you were friends with that guy singing there

134
00:10:47,800 --> 00:10:50,750
since elementary school?

135
00:10:50,750 --> 00:10:56,260
I parted ways with my friends after I went to college.

136
00:10:56,260 --> 00:10:59,040
You can go to college with your best friend,

137
00:10:59,040 --> 00:11:00,730
I'm envious of that.

138
00:11:16,290 --> 00:11:18,760
You can hold your liquor.

139
00:11:18,760 --> 00:11:21,390
I didn't know either.

140
00:11:21,390 --> 00:11:22,990
But it seems like it.

141
00:12:27,100 --> 00:12:29,160
Mom.

142
00:12:31,410 --> 00:12:36,000
I drank for the first time since I was born.

143
00:12:42,340 --> 00:12:44,080
So you liked it?

144
00:12:46,730 --> 00:12:51,940
Of course. I'm a good drinker.

145
00:13:20,870 --> 00:13:25,890
Hey, you can't even drink a bottle.

146
00:13:25,890 --> 00:13:27,920
Don't drink too much next time.

147
00:13:29,370 --> 00:13:31,150
Don't worry. I know it myself.

148
00:13:31,150 --> 00:13:32,910
Well...

149
00:13:34,380 --> 00:13:37,220
This is close to the front gate of the school.

150
00:13:37,220 --> 00:13:39,440
I'm living by myself somewhere near the back gate.

151
00:13:42,140 --> 00:13:46,060
So you moved out.

152
00:13:47,040 --> 00:13:49,580
I told you before.

153
00:13:49,580 --> 00:13:52,780
By the way, give me your schedule.

154
00:13:54,080 --> 00:13:55,220
Why?

155
00:13:55,220 --> 00:13:56,730
What do you mean?

156
00:13:56,730 --> 00:14:00,180
We should do the things we agreed on doing after getting into university one by one.

157
00:14:13,520 --> 00:14:14,480
Yoojae.

158
00:14:14,480 --> 00:14:16,040
Wait.

159
00:14:19,020 --> 00:14:20,900
I'll go first.

160
00:14:23,080 --> 00:14:24,630
Okay.

161
00:14:27,900 --> 00:14:30,210
I've thought about it for a long time.

162
00:14:32,720 --> 00:14:35,560
If you really like me,

163
00:14:38,330 --> 00:14:40,900
would you do this to me?

164
00:14:45,850 --> 00:14:48,630
You suddenly disappeared like smoke.

165
00:14:52,250 --> 00:14:54,960
Have you ever thought about my feelings?

166
00:15:00,600 --> 00:15:01,970
I'm sorry.

167
00:15:06,410 --> 00:15:07,860
I'm sorry.

168
00:15:10,820 --> 00:15:12,300
Since you're sorry,

169
00:15:12,300 --> 00:15:14,430
let's be friends.

170
00:15:21,440 --> 00:15:23,930
How have you been?

171
00:15:23,930 --> 00:15:28,630
What? Just like that.

172
00:15:28,630 --> 00:15:31,210
Do you work part-time often?

173
00:15:31,210 --> 00:15:37,030
Of course. I'm tutoring and doing food delivery.

174
00:15:37,030 --> 00:15:40,940
I work part-time in the neighborhood while riding a bike. It earns well.

175
00:15:42,150 --> 00:15:43,880
You must have made a lot of money.

176
00:15:43,880 --> 00:15:46,880
Of course. Look at the conditions around.

177
00:15:46,880 --> 00:15:49,640
The room is warm. I don't even catch a cold now.

178
00:15:50,340 --> 00:15:52,250
Good boy.

179
00:15:53,700 --> 00:15:59,990
Well... The clothes are pretty.

180
00:16:01,870 --> 00:16:05,650
This one? I just bought it.

181
00:16:07,860 --> 00:16:10,750
But sneakers don't match your clothes.

182
00:16:12,420 --> 00:16:14,720
Why don't you buy a pair of sneakers too?

183
00:16:15,840 --> 00:16:18,800
I'm going to buy them.

184
00:16:18,800 --> 00:16:20,810
Come with me tomorrow?

185
00:16:21,790 --> 00:16:23,540
Okay.

186
00:16:26,370 --> 00:16:29,020
I'm leaving now.

187
00:16:29,020 --> 00:16:30,090
Okay. Bye.

188
00:16:30,090 --> 00:16:30,990
Call me tomorrow.

189
00:16:30,990 --> 00:16:32,420
Okay.

190
00:16:40,380 --> 00:16:43,830
I took it out to throw it away.

191
00:16:45,410 --> 00:16:48,580
Can I throw it for you?

192
00:16:48,580 --> 00:16:51,070
What? Sure.

193
00:17:02,280 --> 00:17:04,040
Bye.

194
00:17:04,040 --> 00:17:06,109
Bye. Take care.

195
00:18:03,420 --> 00:18:08,500
[Star Struck]
